name: Nemours Children's Health, Downtown Orlando, Specialty Care

narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Nemours Children's Health, Downtown Orlando, Specialty Care is a Clinic/Center, Multi-Specialty provider based in Orlando, FL. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $44.4M in Medicaid payments across 424K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $44.4M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
